---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Privacy Policy - DraftOne"
  description="DraftOne privacy policy - how we collect, use, and protect your personal information."
>
  <section class="privacy-content">
    <div class="content-wrapper">
      <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="last-updated">Last updated: February 28, 2026</p>

      <div class="policy-section">
        <h2>Introduction</h2>
        <p>
          DraftOne ("we," "our," or "us") respects your privacy and is committed to protecting your personal information. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and safeguard your information when you visit our website or use our services.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="policy-section">
        <h2>Information We Collect</h2>
        <p>When you sign up for our waitlist, we collect:</p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Email address</strong> (required) - to notify you when DraftOne launches</li>
          <li><strong>First name</strong> (optional) - to personalize communications</li>
        </ul>
        <p>We do not collect any other personal information through our website at this time.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="policy-section">
        <h2>How We Use Your Information</h2>
        <p>We use your information solely to:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Send you updates about DraftOne's launch and development</li>
          <li>Respond to your inquiries or feedback</li>
          <li>Improve our website and services</li>
        </ul>
        <p>We will never sell, rent, or share your personal information with third parties for marketing purposes.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="policy-section">
        <h2>Email Communications</h2>
        <p>
          By joining our waitlist, you consent to receive emails from us about DraftOne. You can unsubscribe at any time by clicking the "unsubscribe" link at the bottom of any email we send you.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="policy-section">
        <h2>Data Storage and Security</h2>
        <p>
          Your information is stored securely through Mailchimp, our email service provider. Mailchimp is compliant with GDPR, CCPA, and other privacy regulations. We implement appropriate security measures to protect your information from unauthorized access, alteration, or disclosure.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="policy-section">
        <h2>Cookies and Tracking</h2>
        <p>
          Our website does not use cookies or tracking technologies at this time. We do not collect analytics or behavioral data.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="policy-section">
        <h2>Your Rights</h2>
        <p>You have the right to:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Access the personal information we hold about you</li>
          <li>Request correction of inaccurate information</li>
          <li>Request deletion of your information</li>
          <li>Opt out of email communications at any time</li>
        </ul>
        <p>
          To exercise these rights, please contact us at <a href="mailto:privacy@draftone.com">privacy@draftone.com</a>.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="policy-section">
        <h2>Children's Privacy</h2>
        <p>
          Our services are not directed to children under 13. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children under 13. If you believe we have collected information from a child under 13, please contact us immediately.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="policy-section">
        <h2>Changes to This Policy</h2>
        <p>
          We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Changes will be posted on this page with an updated "Last updated" date. We encourage you to review this policy periodically.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="policy-section">
        <h2>Contact Us</h2>
        <p>
          If you have questions about this Privacy Policy or our data practices, please contact us at:
        </p>
        <p>
          <strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:privacy@draftone.com">privacy@draftone.com</a>
        </p>
      </div>

      <p class="back-link"><a href="/">← Back to Home</a></p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .privacy-content {
    padding: var(--space-12) var(--space-4);
    min-height: 100vh;
  }

  .content-wrapper {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  h1 {
    font-size: var(--text-4xl);
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-2);
    color: var(--text-primary);
  }

  .last-updated {
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-8);
  }

  .policy-section {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-8);
  }

  .policy-section h2 {
    font-size: var(--text-2xl);
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-3);
    color: var(--text-primary);
  }

  .policy-section p {
    font-size: var(--text-base);
    line-height: 1.75;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-3);
  }

  .policy-section ul {
    margin: var(--space-3) 0;
    padding-left: var(--space-6);
  }

  .policy-section li {
    font-size: var(--text-base);
    line-height: 1.75;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-2);
  }

  .policy-section a {
    color: var(--accent-primary);
    text-decoration: underline;
    transition: color var(--transition-fast);
  }

  .policy-section a:hover {
    color: var(--accent-primary-hover);
  }

  .back-link {
    margin-top: var(--space-12);
    text-align: center;
  }

  .back-link a {
    color: var(--accent-primary);
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 500;
    transition: color var(--transition-fast);
  }

  .back-link a:hover {
    color: var(--accent-primary-hover);
    text-decoration: underline;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .privacy-content {
      padding: var(--space-16) var(--space-6);
    }

    h1 {
      font-size: var(--text-5xl);
    }
  }
</style>
